  "description": "Product Description ENJSD 100\" Extendable Microfiber Feather Duster for Cleaning High Ceiling Fans Blinds Cobweb Why Choose ENJSD Extendable Feather Duseter? Extendable 100'' Microfiber Feather Duster for Cleaning High Ceiling Fans Blinds Cobweb Electrostatic Adsorption Duster Washable and Flexible to Fold It 90┬░as You Need Can Be Easily Hang on The Hook and Storage ENJSD Feather Duster is Your Best Choice! Make Your Housework more Easy and Quickly Extendable 100 '' Pole To Clean the High Place ENJSD feather duster is designed with 100 inches extendable pole, which is different from other short handheld feather dusters. Suitable for cleaning the ceiling,ceiling fan,ceiling light and bookshelf. Also the high windows in your house, warehouse, garage. Easily to Clean the Cobweb Bacteria &amp; Dust This kinds of microfiber duster can clean up the cobweb of ceiling corner , anywhere dust and reduce the bacterial growth. Easy for you to clean the house, especially the place having heavy dust. Washable Microfiber Material No need to worry the feather duster become dirty, and not easy to clean it. It is made of microfiber fabric that you can use water to wash it , even add detergent. Convenience for Storage Comes with a hole of handle , feather duster can be hanged on the wall or other places having hook. In addition, it can be disassembled storaging in the drawer or carbinet. Convenience for storage at home. Detachable Duster Head When you need to clean the microfiber duster head, just twist the head, it will detach from the feather duster pole. When you want to storage the duster, do the same way twisting the head, and put the head and pole into the drawer. Strong Electrostatic Adsorption Strong static electricity can absorb dust cobweb easily. ENJSD high quality microfiber head can quickly absorb dust and hair, fast and easy cleaning the large places.Efficient cleaning ability, saving much more time. ENJSD feather duster you deserve one! ENJSD Feather Duster Washable Microfiber duster Cleaning Steps: 1.Rinse the Fibers with Water 2.Apply the Detergent by Hand 3.Rub the Duster in Your Palm and Squeeze Out the Sewage 4.Rinse with Water and Twist Out the Remaining Water 5.Hold Both Ends of the Duster Head with Both Hands and Rotate the Fiber to Make it Easier to Dry Extendable Feather Duster Easy to clean the High Place As you can see above mentioned, this kinds of feather duster having 100'' stainless steel extendable rod that not only can clean the table but also the high place, like ceiling, fan, cupboard and so on. Scratch Resistant Cover Avoid Scratching 100'' Stainless Steel Extendable Rod 90 Degree Bendable Head Hangable Design Easy to Hang on the Wall How To Use? 1. First shake the duster fluffy 2. Secondly twist the duster head into the extendable pole 3. Thirdly fold the duster head to 90┬░ and extend the pole to clean the high corner place 4. After clean the all place, twist the duster head off and cleaned by water. 5. Squeeze the microfiber duster head and shake it then hanging on the hook to dry it. Can be Used in Many Places",
